content: Why doesn't your app automatically logs out when the app is exited, not great security wise.
replyContent:
We understand how annoying that must be, please choose the option to always request for a pin on the app to resolve this issue.

Please follow the steps below to enable this option
1. Navigate to and click on your initials
2. Select security
3. Select transaction Pin
